@startuml

[*] --> PromptPin : Card Inserted

PromptPin --> VerifyPin : PIN Entered
VerifyPin --> Options : PIN Verified Successfully

Options --> ProcessWithdrawal : User Approves Withdrawal

ProcessWithdrawal --> DispenseCash : Cash Dispensed
DispenseCash --> PrintReceipt : Receipt Printed

PrintReceipt --> ReturnCard : Card Returned

ReturnCard --> ResetSystem : System Resets

ResetSystem --> [*] : Ready for Next User

@enduml
